6
00:01:09,810 --> 00:01:13,580
And they like to have
things their way.

7
00:01:13,613 --> 00:01:16,750
And you've got one of the most
successful underground fighting

8
00:01:16,783 --> 00:01:19,787
rings here in Asia.

9
00:01:19,820 --> 00:01:23,757
But you see when
Beijing comes over,

10
