00:26:02,734 --> 00:26:04,069
Las Vegas?

294
00:26:04,102 --> 00:26:05,938
That's the one.

295
00:26:05,971 --> 00:26:09,909
Well I hear that's not
much of a real place either.

296
00:26:09,942 --> 00:26:11,310
You got me there pal.

297
00:26:11,343 --> 00:26:12,044
Coming?

298
00:26:17,382 --> 00:26:19,318
Ah, thanks.

299
00:26:19,351 --> 00:26:20,219
Don't mention it.

300
00:26:46,879 --> 00:26:47,580
Vinnie Vasta.

301
00:26:51,149 --> 00:26:51,884
It's nice to meet you.

302
00:26:55,687 --> 00:26:56,722
