00:27:01,226 --> 00:27:01,928
Paulie.

305
00:27:05,464 --> 00:27:08,166
Paul.

306
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:12,504
So, where you
header, Paulie Paul?

307
00:27:12,537 --> 00:27:13,239
Las Vegas.

308
00:27:16,241 --> 00:27:18,109
