335
00:29:17,796 --> 00:29:21,000
That's your name, isn't it?

336
00:29:21,033 --> 00:29:23,702
Shane McQuade.

337
00:29:23,735 --> 00:29:26,105
Don't you know you're famous?

338
00:29:26,138 --> 00:29:27,840
Famous?

339
00:29:27,873 --> 00:29:30,075
Guess you haven't
