340
00:29:30,108 --> 00:29:32,845
You made front page a
few days back Shane.

341
00:29:32,878 --> 00:29:35,180
You're a one man
killing machine.

342
00:29:35,213 --> 00:29:37,750
First you break some
guys neck, and then you

343
00:29:37,783 --> 00:29:38,650
