344
00:29:38,683 --> 00:29:39,785
I didn't-

345
00:29:39,818 --> 00:29:40,853
Dig Shane.

346
00:29:40,886 --> 00:29:42,053
That's what I brought
you out here for.

347
00:29:47,659 --> 00:29:50,229
Shane McQuade.

348
00:29:50,262 --> 00:29:52,764
How'd you get a name like that?

349
00:29:52,798 --> 00:29:55,467
I got it from a guy who
liked American Westerns.

350
00:29:55,500 --> 00:29:56,335
Huh.

351
00:29:56,368 --> 00:29:58,070
