boss, he'll split a gut.

361
00:30:30,669 --> 00:30:35,407
As soon as we bury this
guy, we'll head into Vegas.

362
00:30:35,440 --> 00:30:36,809
You'll love Vegas.

363
00:30:46,852 --> 00:30:49,688
So, it's gonna be like this?

364
00:30:49,721 --> 00:30:50,489
I guess so.

365
00:32:28,553 --> 00:32:32,424
