dropping in for a chat.

378
00:35:38,543 --> 00:35:39,711
Coincidence?

379
00:35:39,744 --> 00:35:40,612
I think not.

380
00:35:43,548 --> 00:35:44,783
We were best friends once.

381
00:35:44,816 --> 00:35:45,817
Once.

382
00:35:45,850 --> 00:35:47,319
Times change.

383
00:35:47,352 --> 00:35:49,054
You knew me then.

384
00:35:49,087 --> 00:35:50,255
