397
00:36:22,387 --> 00:36:24,323
I want you to have a drink in
your hand when I tell you this.

398
00:36:51,316 --> 00:36:54,119
Hey, you remember Marian?

399
00:36:54,152 --> 00:36:55,987
Marian.

400
00:36:56,020 --> 00:36:56,788
Marian Starret?

401
00:36:56,821 --> 00:37:00,692
Yeah, I bets that's the one.

402
00:37:00,725 --> 00:37:01,726
Damn.

403
00:37:01,759 --> 00:37:04,763
I haven't thought
about her in years.

404
00:37:04,796 --> 00:37:07,632
