00:44:16,961 --> 00:44:20,265
That's right Mr Lee,
we're all square.

492
00:44:27,204 --> 00:44:27,906
Speak.

493
00:44:32,310 --> 00:44:34,979
It's all right.

494
00:44:35,012 --> 00:44:36,714
